443
00:39:44,487 --> 00:39:46,011
Fuj, to je smrad.

444
00:39:54,786 --> 00:39:56,121
Hee Sook.

445
00:40:01,491 --> 00:40:03,029
Si doma?

446
00:40:03,029 --> 00:40:06,842
Yeon Hee, poďme preč.

447
00:40:06,842 --> 00:40:08,485
Prosím.

448
00:40:08,485 --> 00:40:11,266
Dobre, poďme.

449
00:40:11,266 --> 00:40:12,389
Vodu.

450
00:40:15,942 --> 00:40:17,552
Počula si to?

451
00:40:17,552 --> 00:40:19,543
Ja som niečo počula.

452
00:40:27,268 --> 00:40:29,420
Hee Sook, Hee Sook!

